commit.message:
[Rendering] Make sure flattened directories ask icons for the first dir.

The icon for "/src/main/java" is based on "src", not "java".
[Git] Fix incorrect use of git cache when pre-fetching ignored files.
[Persistence] Don't validate that a project exists if it is ignored.

[Git] Strip filename after splitting a line.

Fixes #1084
[Build] Add a build for Emacs 29.2.
[Misc] Bump copyright year.
[Misc] After after-file-visit hook.
[Treelib] Add option to define visit-actions.

[Treelib] Only set mouse actions after the mouse interface was loaded.

Fixes #1073

[Peek] Run peek-mode tear down when quitting treemacs.

Fixes #1063

[Compatibility] Remove disabling of evil-escape.

evil-escape now supports treemacs so it doesn't need to be turned off anymore.
[Treelib] Add option to provide a double-click action.
[Core] Fix potential null pointer.

[Treelib] Let extensions control help-echo

The same as was done for extensions in 0a3d2bd67cfb56468fbeea1e0be86436c049e931

[Core] Handle empty variadic nodes when refreshing.

Fixes #1065

[Core] Don't set default-button category so as not use button-map.

Fixes #1052
[Interface] Fix treemacs-delete-other-windows.

[Core] Un-inline treemacs--file-extension.

Fixes #1051
[Rendering] Ensure flattened directories don't temporarily hide git annotations.

[Git] Correct status update when files are deleted.

Fixes #1064
[Core] Remove manual icon background color setup.
[Treelib] Add on-expand and on-collapse arguments.
[Misc] Explain that stale bot won't close issues.

[Core] Reduce inlining in icon creation.

This should fix bytecode overflow errors during compilation.

[Icons] Correct the determination of icons' types.

Fixes #1061

[Docs] Add examples for custom directory icons.

Fixes #1059
[Git] Update containing dirs' git status when deleting & creating files.
[Rendering] Correct use of inline variables.

[Rendering] Correct insert of single directory nodes.

Fixes #1057
[UI] Don't compile doom-modeline.
